[[div class="skip_window"]]
+  ❝Something smart. ❞

Welcome to my art page! I make art from time to time, mainly one-off pieces and occasional insignias. 

My artwork posted to this site falls under [https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/ Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 3.0 license], so please credit me by linking my page or mentioning my name!
@@ @@
++ ❝Something smart to the second power.❞

I'm [[*user SleepyDancho]], but you can call me Dancho or Sleepy for short. 

I got into SCP content back in 2018 when I fell into a youtube rabbit hole. I've been in love ever since, and have been producing SCP-related art since 2019. My earliest works have been lost to time, but I've been cooking up more and more SCP art in recent years. 

I also take commissions if you're interested in my art. If you'd like to commission me, contact me on Discord, my username there is **SleepyDancho**.
[[/div]]
